data.description: This gorgeouis, custom-built, well-maintained Home is on a large, oversized corner lot in New Ulm.  From the welcoming covered porches to the white exterior with brick skirting, this Farmhouse Style home has tremendous curb appeal.  The open concept floorplan has tons of natural light and high, 11' ceilings to make this a perfect place for entertaining family and friends.  There are marble countertops throughout and elegant oak wood flooring and tile.  The Kitchen has a spacious island detailed with a brick front and stainless-steel appliances.  This great location in the heart of New Ulm is on the way to Round Top for ultimate shopping trips.  It is also just a short drive from the Fall's, Columbus, Cat Spring and Brenham.  Make an appointment today to tour this STUNNING HOME!!!
